title: Furious: Role Model (from DHP 31) (2013) (Digital-1680) (Empire)
description:
This is "Furious: Role Model", a short published in "Dark Horse Presents" issue 31.

Eeever so slightly late, considering that it serves as the lead-in to the five-issue series (  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10254209" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10254209</a>   ) which wrapped up two weeks ago... but better that than never, right? :)

By Bryan Glass (  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_J._L._Glass" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_J._L._Glass</a>   ), creator and writer of "Mice Templar".
